# Spacing Tokens

Semantic spacing aliases referencing the base scale. Use these in CSS via `var(--space-*)` and in Tailwind via arbitrary values `gap-[var(--space-2)]` or mapped utilities.

## Spacing Scale

| Token | Base Scale | Value | Use Case |
|-------|-----------|-------|----------|
| `--space-1` | `--scale-4` | 4px | Micro gaps |
| `--space-2` | `--scale-8` | 8px | Icon padding, tight gaps, inline elements |
| `--space-3` | `--scale-12` | 12px | Form field gaps, small component padding |
| `--space-4` | `--scale-16` | 16px | Standard padding, card gaps, button padding |
| `--space-5` | `--scale-20` | 20px | Medium gaps, card padding (md) |
| `--space-6` | `--scale-24` | 24px | Card padding (lg), section gaps |
| `--space-7` | `--scale-28` | 28px | Component internal spacing |
| `--space-8` | `--scale-32` | 32px | Large component gaps |
| `--space-9` | `--scale-36` | 36px | Section padding |
| `--space-10` | `--scale-40` | 40px | Large spacing |
| `--space-12` | `--scale-48` | 48px | Section margins |
| `--space-16` | `--scale-64` | 64px | Page sections |
| `--space-20` | `--scale-80` | 80px | Hero spacing |
| `--space-24` | `--scale-96` | 96px | Large section breaks |

## Component Sizing Scale

Fixed heights for interactive components:

| Token | Value | Used by |
|-------|-------|---------|
| `--scale-32` | 32px | Button xs |
| `--scale-36` | 36px | Switch sm track, InputGroup sm |
| `--scale-40` | 40px | Button sm, TextInput sm, Dropdown sm |
| `--scale-44` | 44px | Switch md track, InputGroup md, min tap target |
| `--scale-48` | 48px | Button md, TextInput md, Dropdown md |
| `--scale-52` | 52px | InputGroup lg |
| `--scale-56` | 56px | Button lg, TextInput lg, Dropdown lg |
| `--scale-64` | 64px | Button xl |

## Tailwind Mapping

In Tailwind, prefer standard utilities where they match, and arbitrary values for token references:

| CSS property | Tailwind approach |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `gap: var(--space-2)` | `gap-2` (8px matches) or `gap-[var(--space-2)]` |
| `padding: var(--space-4)` | `p-4` (16px matches) or `p-[var(--space-4)]` |
| `height: var(--scale-48)` | `h-12` (48px matches) |
| `height: var(--scale-40)` | `h-10` (40px matches) |
| `height: var(--scale-56)` | `h-14` (56px matches) |

Spacing tokens are **theme-agnostic** — they do not change between light and dark themes.

## Inter-Component Spacing (Quick Reference)

| Between | Spacing |
|---------|---------|
| Label and input | `--space-2` (8px) |
| Input and helper/error text | `--space-2` (8px) |
| Form fields | `--space-5` (20px) |
| Section heading and content | `--space-8` (32px) |
| Cards in a grid | `--space-4` mobile, `--space-6` desktop |
| Buttons in a group | `--space-3` (12px) |
| Icon and adjacent text | `--space-2` (8px) |

## Responsive Breakpoints

| Name | Width | Layout |
|------|-------|--------|
| Mobile | < 640px | Single column, full-width buttons |
| Tablet | 640–1024px | Two columns where appropriate |
| Desktop | > 1024px | Max content 1200px, multi-column |
